game.name: Vanellope Injured Emergency
game.description:
Cute Rebel Vanellope participated in the most popular cart racing. She was pretty unlucky today and her car lost the balance on the terrain and was thrown into the trench. Her friends were there and rushed her to your hospital immediately. The good news is that she had only a few small fractures and few bruises. Being the best doctor in the hospital, you have decided to take care of this task. Join Vanellope Injured Emergency and be prepared to provide her the best treatment for her injury!

Grab all your medical tools and get ready to treat the baby in this one of the best HTML5 doctor games for girls! Find out all the broken bones in her body using the X-Ray machine and then get ready to place casts on the right spots! Begin the process with grabbing a tissue and wiping out all the dirt accumulated on her injured body! Clear the blood in her nose and the tears in her eyes with the tissue paper! Collect a stethoscope to check out her heartbeat!

Clear the dirt by pouring some eye drops in her eyes and use a pair of tweezers to remove the glass shards in her skin! You can prevent the infections by applying some ointment on her wounds. Make sure that you have placed the bandages on her wounds to heal them faster. Once it is done, do not forget to use some vaccines to help her prevent any other diseases. Show all your intense doctoring abilities to take care of her wounds and fractures in the best way possible! Play more baby girls games on our website for free and have fun with your friends without download!
